commandes :
- dotnet new webapi -n CustomerWebApi
- dotnet sln add CustomerWebApi/CustomerWebApi.csproj
- dotnet build CustomerWebApi/CustomerWebApi.csproj

nuget :
- dotnet add CustomerWebApi/CustomerWebApi.csproj package FluentValidation.AspNetCore
- dotnet add CustomerWebApi/CustomerWebApi.csproj package AutoMapper.Extensions.Microsoft.DependencyInjection
- dotnet add CustomerWebApi/CustomerWebApi.csproj package MediatR
- dotnet add CustomerWebApi/CustomerWebApi.csproj package Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore
- dotnet add CustomerWebApi/CustomerWebApi.csproj package Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.InMemory
- dotnet add CustomerWebApi/CustomerWebApi.csproj package FluentValidation.AspNetCore
- dotnet add CustomerWebApi/CustomerWebApi.csproj package Swashbuckle.AspNetCore

- dotnet add CustomerWebApi/CustomerWebApi.csproj package MediatR.Extensions.Microsoft.DependencyInjection

